product_name: MaybellineSuper Stay Vinyl Ink Liquid Lipcolor
summary: SummaryHighlightsClean IngredientsVeganGive BackShake up your longwear with Maybelline's budge-resistant Super Stay Vinyl Ink Liquid Lipcolor. With up to 16HR wear, the color Lock formula defies smudging and transfer. Gives lips instant shine, just shake and swipe.
details: DetailsBenefitsDelivers no-budge vinyl color & up to 16-hour wearColor lock formula defies smudging & transferSwipe the comfortable formula on your lips for an instant shineAvailable in various vinyl shades for your every look, from loud pinks & berries to the everyday neutrals and saturated red tonesFeaturesFormulated with caring ingredients which help provide a comfortable feelContains no animal derived ingredients or by-productsItem 2596491How To UseTo apply, simply shake and swipe the product on your lips. Shake for at least five seconds before applying. Apply as you normally would to clean, dry lips using its precise flocked tip applicator and let fully dry.Flammable until dry. Do not use near fire, flame, or heat.IngredientsIsododecane, Dimethicone, Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Polymethylsilsesquioxane/Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Polypropylsilsesquioxane, C30-45 Alkyldimethylsilyl Polypropylsilsesquioxane, Trimethylsiloxyphenyl Dimethicone, Trimethyl Pentaphenyl Trisiloxane, Bis-Stearyl Dimethicone, Dimethiconol, Trihydroxystearin, Phenoxyethanol, Alumina, Ethylhexylglycerin, Tocopheryl Acetate, Triethoxycaprylylsilane, Limonene, Isopropyl Palmitate, Isopropyl Myristate, Silica, Benzyl Benzoate, Benzyl Alcohol, Citronellol, Linalool, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Extract, Tocopherol, Parfum/Fragrance. May Contain (+/-): Ci 77891/Titanium Dioxide, Ci 15850/Red 7, Ci 77491, Ci 77492, Ci 77499/Iron Oxides, Ci 45410/Red 28 Lake, Ci 45380/Red 22 Lake, Ci 15985/Yellow 6 Lake, Ci 19140/Yellow 5 Lake, Ci 17200/Red 33 Lake, Ci 15850/Red 6, Ci 77742/Manganese Violet, Ci 42090/Blue 1 Lake. Fil T286301/1.Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsShipping Restrictions : This item cannot be shipped via air.
how_to_use: To apply, simply shake and swipe the product on your lips. Shake for at least five seconds before applying. Apply as you normally would to clean, dry lips using its precise flocked tip applicator and let fully dry.Flammable until dry. Do not use near fire, flame, or heat.

reviews.headline: Lasts All Day!
reviews.comments: Not only does is wear perfectly all day, but even through drinking and eating throughout the day also! No touch ups needed!

reviews.headline: Stays on all day.
reviews.comments: This product works great. The only issue I have is when it runs out of color it comes out as just gloss without warning you are just out of color. It stays on all day does'nt get on cups or glasses etc. I love it.

reviews.headline: Love it!
reviews.comments: This lipstick lasts even longer than I expected! I'm definitely buying it again

reviews.headline: I will buy this again.
reviews.comments: love the matte look

reviews.headline: I would buy this again.
reviews.comments: Love the color and it goes on soft and smooth  on the lips

reviews.headline: I will buy it again
reviews.comments: Very goof product

reviews.headline: I love it
reviews.comments: i like it!!!!

reviews.headline: not worth it
reviews.comments: When i first bought this I loved it. After a month of using it though, no pigment was coming out, only a sheer lipgloss (even after shaking it for 5 mins)

reviews.headline: My "Go To" lipgloss
reviews.comments: This is hands-down my favorite lip product. One application and it lasts all day; through meals, drinks, napkins, and even kisses, without smearing or transferring. My lips never feel dry or cracked. I've ditched expensive brands because this is my go-to. Only wish there were more shades!

reviews.headline: Stays!
reviews.comments: Love this in the burgundy.  Unlike most long lasting lipsticks this one does not dry your lips out or look cakey.

reviews.headline: I like it a lot
reviews.comments: When you first get the product its a bit much and can get on your teeth but after a few uses it works perfectly. It wipes off kind of easy near the inside of your lips sometimes and looks weird. Color is super pigmented and works great otherwise

reviews.headline: Didn't care for colors
reviews.comments: Bought 2 units of this lipstick. The colors don't match the chart. Don't like either one. Wish I could return.

reviews.headline: Great product
reviews.comments: It actually stays on all day and night without reapplying

reviews.headline: If you line your lips, this is for you.
reviews.comments: Coy looked a little purple on me but when i blended it into my liner and it was SEAMLESS I knew I made the right choice. Will be wearing this until i run out. WE NEED MORE COLORS!!!

reviews.headline: Stains Teeth
reviews.comments: Love the color and formula. But the stain goes on my teeth. Even after the color is gone.

reviews.headline: I Finally Found the ONE!!!!
reviews.comments: Omg, I found a product that I don't need to be putting over and over when I go out. 100% recommended it doesn't remove like any others. Your lips will look super awesome all day no matter if you drink , use napkins, it's just great. I love it and looking forward to purchase much more colors.

reviews.headline: Both items were already open
reviews.comments: The lipstick arrived unsealed, which is a hygiene concern. I did not use or open it.

reviews.headline: I liked it
reviews.comments: I returned it as the color was way too dark. I thought it would be sheer because it was liquid but it has a lot of pigment. I got a lighter shade.

reviews.headline: Love this
reviews.comments: This is an excellent product!  Not drying at all.  Lasts me a long time through food and drinks.  Cheeky is the perfect neutral color!

reviews.headline: Maybeline Super Stay Vinyl Lipcolor
reviews.comments: I haven't used it much. I am trying to find something for my wedding that won't transfer on napkins or glasses. This product seems to be ok but I have to let it fully dry.

faceoff_positive.comments: I purchased the colors peachy and cheeky after watching Mikayla Noguiera's review on TikTok and I'm glad I did. These lipsticks are beautiful! The colors are pigmented and glossy without feeling sticky. They feel lightweight and last all day. The packaging is so boogie and expensive looking. 10 out of 10!
faceoff_positive.headline: Beautiful and shiny!

faceoff_negative.comments: So disappointed!   Shook well, applied, then waited for it to dry.  And waited....and waited some more.  At 10 minutes it was still a sticky mess.  As I sit here 30 minutes later after blotting it on paper, it's still sticky
faceoff_negative.headline: Sticky!
